  <title>Cost with Price Breaks</title>
  <metadata>
  <md:content-id>m31064</md:content-id><md:title>Cost with Price Breaks</md:title>
  <md:abstract>A general pattern for costs with price breaks is set up and an application is made in the case demand D has a Poisson distribution.</md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>f28fc9d8-6dc6-4e22-8c1c-09aa2c29fc88</md:uuid>
</metadata>
